        "body": "<p>Can someone explain me the following code step by step:<\/p>\n\n<p>I can not understand, for example:  <code>while(0&lt;=--_)$+=(¢.charAt(_)-0x30)&lt;&lt;(_&amp;01l);<\/code> <\/p>\n\n<p>This code is working very fine, But I couldn't understand the code.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public String multiply(String ¢) {\n    int $=0,_=¢.length();\n    while(0&lt;=--_)$+=(¢.charAt(_)-0x30)&lt;&lt;(_&amp;01l);\n    return Integer.toString($);\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
